AUDIO: 'Here\'s some examples on the windows. So, this is the example of the middle exposure that it brought out in the camera that it decided was the average lit scene for this. Now, if you just did a 3-2,'

[02:33] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'this one and this one would be the exposures afterwards. So, the middle would be perfect or what, you know, the average scene collects, and then you can see outside the windows clearly in this one,'

