VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'here and was really bright on the countertop, it took care of that really easily. All of these little window spots up here, nice and cut out. So, this is a perfect shot. Remember, ambient is best for Photello, and then doing it on a'

[06:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'tripod is also best. So, I would turn your ISO as a low as it can go, put it on a tripod, and do either a 5-2 or a 3-2 bracket in aperture priority with your settings on average metering for'

